      "text": "Pateizeet tam KUNgam/ jo winna Schehlastiba paleek muhschigt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pateizeet tam Deewam winnu Deewu/ jo winna Schehlastiba paleek muhschigt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pateizeet tam KUNgam winnu Kungu/ jo winna Schehlastiba paleek muhschigt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas leelus Brihnumus darra weens pats/ jo winna Schehlastiba paleek muhschigt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas tahs Debbeﬁs ar Sa-prafchann padarrijs/ jo winna Schehlastiba paleek muhschigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas to Semmi pahr teem Uhdenim isplattijs/ jo winna Schehlastiba paleek muhschigt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas leelus Spihdettus darrijs/ jo winna Schehlastiba paleek muhschigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "To Sauli/ to Deenu wal-dihjt/ jo winna Schehlastiba pa-leek muhschigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "To Mehnesi un Swatg-nes/ to Nakti waldiht/ jo win-na Schehlastiba paleek muh-schigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas teem Egiptereem ta-wus Pirmdsimmuschus kawe/ jo winna Schehlastiba paleek muhschigt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un irr Israëlu zaur win-na Widdu isweddis/ jo winna Schehlastiba paleek muhschigt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ar stipru Rohku un is-steepu Elkonn/ jo winna Scheh-lastiba paleek muhschigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kas to Needras-Juhra/ jo winna Schehlastiba paleek muhschigt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wedde Israëlu zaur winnas Widdu/ jo winna Schehlastiba paleek muhschigt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un gabse Waräü ar win-na Karra-Spehku Needras-Juh-ra/ jo winna Schehlastiba paleek muhschigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas fatuns Laudis zaur Tukfneft waddija/ jo winna Schehlastiba paleek muhschigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas leelus Kehnittus ka-we/ jo winna Schehlastiba paleek muhschigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un nokawe warrenus Kehnittus/ jo winna Schehlasti-ba paleek muhschigt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Sionu/ to Amoriteeu Kehnittu/ jo winna Schehlasti-ba paleek muhschigt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ogu/ to Kehnittu no Babsana/ jo winna Schehlasti-ba paleek muhschigt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un detwe winnu Semini var Eemantoschann/ jo winna Schehlastiba paleek muhschigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bar Eemantoschanu J-fraektam sawam Kalpam/ jo win-na Schehlastiba paleek muh-schigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas muhfu irr atminnejees eeksch muhsahn Behdahin/ jo winna Schehlastiba paleek muhschigi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un irr muhs no muhseem Prettineekem isrähwis/ jo win-na Schehlastiba paleek muhschigt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas wiffai Meetai Bar-Ifffffff 2 ribu\n"
    }
